---
// TrustBar: fullscreen editorial carousel — large title left, illustration right.
// Active card = full viewport; next card = small preview peeking from the right.
---

<section data-trustbar class="relative bg-brand-dark" style="height: 100vh;">
  <div data-trustbar-inner class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">

    <!-- ── Card 0: Directo ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="trustbar-card absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark" data-card-index="0">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col lg:flex-row">

        <!-- Left: editorial text -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center px-5 sm:px-12 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 pt-20 pb-10 lg:py-0 lg:w-[44%] shrink-0 text-center lg:text-left order-2 lg:order-1 relative z-10">
          <span class="font-mono text-6xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white/[0.06] leading-none select-none block -mb-4 -ml-1">01</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight mb-4">
            Directo
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
            Contacta directamente con el especialista que eliges. Sin llamadas, sin intermediarios, sin esperas.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="#funcionalidades" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors">
              Saber más
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: illustration -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center p-8 lg:p-12 order-1 lg:order-2 relative overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Gradient blend: left edge fades into card bg -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bottom-0 w-16 lg:w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-dark to-transparent pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
          <div class="w-64 sm:w-72 lg:w-80 xl:w-96 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden select-none pointer-events-none">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-100 bg-slate-50">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold text-primary-700 shrink-0">GL</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-navy">Dr. García López</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-primary-500 font-medium">● En línea</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-end gap-2">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold text-primary-700 shrink-0">GL</div>
                <div class="max-w-[75%] bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl rounded-bl-sm px-3 py-2 text-xs text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Hola, he revisado la documentación. Le recomendaría una consulta presencial.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-end gap-2 flex-row-reverse">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold text-white shrink-0">Tú</div>
                <div class="max-w-[75%] bg-primary-600 rounded-2xl rounded-br-sm px-3 py-2 text-xs text-white leading-relaxed">Muchas gracias doctor, ¿cuándo tiene disponibilidad?</div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-end gap-2">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold text-primary-700 shrink-0">GL</div>
                <div class="max-w-[75%] bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl rounded-bl-sm px-3 py-2 text-xs text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">El jueves a las 17:00 tengo hueco. ¿Le viene bien?</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-slate-100 px-3 py-2.5 bg-white">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl px-3 py-2">
                <div class="flex-1 text-[10px] text-slate-300">Escribe un mensaje...</div>
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-lg bg-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Card 1: Verificados ────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="trustbar-card absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark" data-card-index="1">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col lg:flex-row">

        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center px-5 sm:px-12 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 pt-20 pb-10 lg:py-0 lg:w-[44%] shrink-0 text-center lg:text-left order-2 lg:order-1 relative z-10">
          <span class="font-mono text-6xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white/[0.06] leading-none select-none block -mb-4 -ml-1">02</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight mb-4">
            Verificados
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
            Cada perfil muestra el número de colegiado oficial. Sabes exactamente quién es el profesional antes de escribirle.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="#funcionalidades" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors">
              Saber más
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center p-8 lg:p-12 order-1 lg:order-2 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bottom-0 w-16 lg:w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-dark to-transparent pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
          <div class="w-64 sm:w-72 lg:w-80 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden select-none pointer-events-none">
            <div class="h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-50 relative">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold text-primary-700 border-4 border-white absolute -bottom-8 left-5">GL</div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-10 px-5 pb-5">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
                <p class="text-base font-bold text-brand-navy">Dr. García López</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1 bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-primary-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/></svg>
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-primary-700">Verificado</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">Cardiólogo</p>
              <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 mb-4">Col. nº 28-12345 · Madrid</p>
              <div class="flex gap-2 mb-4">
                <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-2.5 text-center border border-slate-100">
                  <p class="text-base font-bold text-brand-navy">4.9</p>
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">Valoración</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-2.5 text-center border border-slate-100">
                  <p class="text-base font-bold text-brand-navy">12+</p>
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">Años exp.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-2.5 text-center border border-slate-100">
                  <p class="text-base font-bold text-brand-navy">80€</p>
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">Consulta</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <div class="flex-1 h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg"></div>
                <div class="flex-1 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Card 2: PWA ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="trustbar-card absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark" data-card-index="2">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col lg:flex-row">

        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center px-5 sm:px-12 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 pt-20 pb-10 lg:py-0 lg:w-[44%] shrink-0 text-center lg:text-left order-2 lg:order-1 relative z-10">
          <span class="font-mono text-6xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white/[0.06] leading-none select-none block -mb-4 -ml-1">03</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight mb-4">
            PWA
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
            Instala EncuentraDoc en tu móvil directamente desde el navegador. Sin App Store ni Google Play.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="#funcionalidades" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors">
              Saber más
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center p-8 lg:p-12 order-1 lg:order-2 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bottom-0 w-16 lg:w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-dark to-transparent pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
          <div class="w-64 sm:w-72 lg:w-72 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden select-none pointer-events-none">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100">
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-300"></span>
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-300"></span>
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-300"></span>
              <div class="flex-1 ml-2 h-5 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full text-[9px] text-slate-400 flex items-center px-3">encuentradoc.com</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-primary-200/60">
                <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">
                  <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.3"/>
                  <path d="M16 8v16M8 16h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-navy mb-1">Añadir a pantalla de inicio</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">encuentradoc.com</p>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full bg-primary-600 rounded-xl py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white">Instalar</div>
              <div class="w-full bg-slate-50 rounded-xl py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 border border-slate-100">Ahora no</div>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-300 text-center">Sin App Store · Sin Google Play</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Card 3: Privacidad ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="trustbar-card absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark" data-card-index="3">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col lg:flex-row">

        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center px-5 sm:px-12 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 pt-20 pb-10 lg:py-0 lg:w-[44%] shrink-0 text-center lg:text-left order-2 lg:order-1 relative z-10">
          <span class="font-mono text-6xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white/[0.06] leading-none select-none block -mb-4 -ml-1">04</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight mb-4">
            Privacidad
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
            Tú decides quién puede ver tu historial médico. Control total sobre tu información, siempre bajo tu mando.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="#funcionalidades" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors">
              Saber más
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center p-8 lg:p-12 order-1 lg:order-2 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bottom-0 w-16 lg:w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-dark to-transparent pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
          <div class="w-64 sm:w-72 lg:w-80 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden select-none pointer-events-none">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 px-5 py-4 border-b border-slate-100">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 border border-primary-200 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-navy">Privacidad y Datos</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 space-y-4">
              {[
                { label: 'Compartir historial', sub: 'Solo médicos verificados', on: true },
                { label: 'Notificaciones', sub: 'Solo mensajes directos', on: true },
                { label: 'Datos de localización', sub: 'Para búsquedas cercanas', on: false },
                { label: 'Marketing', sub: 'Comunicaciones comerciales', on: false },
              ].map((row) => (
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                  <div class="min-w-0">
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-navy">{row.label}</p>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">{row.sub}</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class={`w-9 h-5 rounded-full shrink-0 flex items-center px-0.5 ${row.on ? 'bg-primary-500 justify-end' : 'bg-slate-200 justify-start'}`}>
                    <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-white rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5">
              <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-[11px] text-primary-700 font-medium text-center">
                Tus datos nunca se venden a terceros
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Progress dots overlay -->
    <div data-trustbar-dots
         class="absolute bottom-6 right-8 sm:right-12 lg:right-16 z-[60] flex items-center gap-2"
         aria-hidden="true">
      <div data-dot="0" class="h-1 rounded-full transition-all duration-300" style="width:1.5rem; background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);"></div>
      <div data-dot="1" class="h-1 rounded-full transition-all duration-300" style="width:0.375rem; background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);"></div>
      <div data-dot="2" class="h-1 rounded-full transition-all duration-300" style="width:0.375rem; background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);"></div>
      <div data-dot="3" class="h-1 rounded-full transition-all duration-300" style="width:0.375rem; background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);"></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
